sentences.sContent: The company carries a variety of binders that can be imprinted with your message or logo.
sentences.sCn: 该公司经营各种可以印上客户所需信息或标识的活页夹。

synos.tran: 印记；[法]痕迹；特征；版本说明

remMethod.val: im(不) + print(印记) → 留下印记 → 盖印

words.tran: 铭记（动物生命早期即起作用的一种学习机能）；胚教

trans.tranOther: If a surface is imprinted with a mark or design, that mark or design is printed on the surface or pressed into it
